    <h1>CoreSense</h1>
    
    <h2>The Intelligent Health Vest</h2>
    
    <p>Empowering Your Health with Smart Technology</p>

    <h3>Features</h3>

    <p><b>Posture Detection:</b> Detects slouching and reminds you to sit or stand upright.</p>
    
    <p><b>Heart Rate Monitoring:</b> Tracks your heart rate in real time.</p>
    
    <p><b>Body Heat Regulation:</b> Cools or heats based on your body temperature.</p>
    
    <p><b>Smart Insights:</b> Shows your posture, heart rate, and temperature in the app.</p>
    
    <p><b>Customizable Settings:</b> Lets you change vibration strength and alerts.</p>

    <p><i>CoreSense - Smart. Comfortable. Connected.</i></p>

